| **Protected Badge** | Yellow badge with lock icon | 🔒 Protected |
| **Edit Button** | ✅ **VISIBLE & ENABLED** | Main admin can edit themselves |
| **Reset Password Button** | ✅ **VISIBLE & ENABLED** | Main admin can reset their password |
| **Deactivate Button** | ❌ **HIDDEN** (using `*ngIf`) | Not shown for main admin |
